<span id="freeTextContainer1147034526516654915">Peretti is good at coming up with some creative ideas for stories and this was another good one. It centers around a small out of the way town with a mysterious death. The brother of the deceased wants to look into the circumstances and see what is the cause. Low and behold he hears stories of a dragon. Wait, what? A dragon? Yep. It wasn&apos;t the best book ever but it was enjoyable.</span>
  <span id="freeText1147034526516654915" style="display:none">Peretti is good at coming up with some creative ideas for stories and this was another good one. It centers around a small out of the way town with a mysterious death. The brother of the deceased wants to look into the circumstances and see what is the cause. Low and behold he hears stories of a dragon. Wait, what? A dragon? Yep. It wasn't the best book ever but it was enjoyable.</span>
